We are looking for a passionate Global Mobility Lead to join our dynamitic company! As a Global Mobility Lead you will create the blueprint for our global mobility program. The program will oversee the global relocation, global immigration, tax mobility, extended business travel, short- and long-term assignment programs and our Deployment teams. This small but amazing team is working hard to build a comprehensive and world class global mobility program at Anduril that aligns with business needs and goals while supporting both new and existing employees in their mobility experience. Work cross functionally with key global mobility stakeholders (HR, Employment Law, Corporate Tax, Equity, Payroll, Benefits, Recruiting) to establish streamlined processes, clear guidelines, and meaningful resources. 
